{"tid":327433,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"咩叫高燈？","createTime":"2017-07-18T18:10:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-22T06:35:08.000Z","uid":57840,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"98499bc3bd11995c0386224a65e7d9725b277441","tid":327433,"uid":57840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T18:10:25.000Z","msg":"見到幾次有人開post話多高燈撚都有人唔知咩係高燈，我想講返俾各位新車主知，等大家都唔好犯錯，路上少誤會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">高燈=\\=大燈</span><br />\n高燈係通常係荒山野嶺冇街燈嘅地方先會開<br />\n即係話平時99%都唔會用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點開？</span><br />\n長著--&gt;軚盤邊打燈支棍向車頭方向推<br />\n閃--&gt; 支棍向自己拉 (同噴水一樣)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">點知係咪開左？</span><br />\n1. 俵版上面會有藍色燈<br />\n2. 望吓條路啲路牌係咪反晒光<br />\n3. 望吓前面架車係咪好光<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我真係大燈咋喎，點解都chaang到人</span><br />\n唔該去車房check check你頭燈，己所不欲 勿施於人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efc5c99cfc0ea59c3c63c7f58ffbd458dab77221","tid":327433,"uid":2506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T00:27:36.000Z","msg":"推上去比多d人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f308c63d0f63b494687700ac5521d0b5b7ffe9","tid":327433,"uid":32028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T01:36:28.000Z","msg":"我唔會再返去架啦, 而家連登幾好"},{"pid":"e76b7f621ac3db240e9d2d95ec84bc865a24ba8d","tid":327433,"uid":74210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T01:40:32.000Z","msg":"真係要備多D人睇到呢個post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2e0230a3fbdc25e5797076972d777377d7f3992","tid":327433,"uid":73123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T01:43:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係要備多D人睇到呢個post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n早兩日大雨到開盡水潑都唔係咁睇到路，對面線仲有個仆街開高燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更加睇唔到路，佢老母臭閪生左條仆街出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"466d22cc7c6d40bc2d2966a38e668ef79a337972","tid":327433,"uid":57840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T01:58:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真係要備多D人睇到呢個post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n早兩日大雨到開盡水潑都唔係咁睇到路，對面線仲有個仆街開高燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更加睇唔到路，佢老母臭閪生左條仆街出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多人以為開高燈睇清楚啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實仲差<br />\n香港啲路好光，根本開燈都只係為左俾其他車見到你頭尾燈"},{"pid":"b93325070685a4b37fa4a2ab2863b195732d40ea","tid":327433,"uid":53520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T01:59:48.000Z","msg":"屌，尋日係吐公收工時間已經車又多又落大雨，重比後面架r佛射到眼都盲埋"},{"pid":"6e6cd73b98d41b254b8ba1bcbbc2656ae97b7a57","tid":327433,"uid":20602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T04:14:18.000Z","msg":"而家就算唔係高燈, HID燈都好「橙」眼。有時夜晚對面線開左大燈都中太陽拳"},{"pid":"97b1ddbe84a5093ee0f27f3ea88e39d81fa62e70","tid":327433,"uid":78122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T04:26:11.000Z","msg":"另外講多樣<br />\n其實大部份車都有得較燈影<br />\n自己知自己係HID嘅盡量較低啲唔好直射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d3d9f581ecd081e88012f0b1c965b5ad6f97f32","tid":327433,"uid":2764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T04:46:15.000Z","msg":"新車果d全部太陽拳<br />\n停係佢車尾果盞煞車燈光撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d3acfcec34ebfd4ce43eca363e32d73a30c839","tid":327433,"uid":103011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T04:51:51.000Z","msg":"係隧道入邊開高燈嗰啲先on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abae0de935e783431357c274a6a06b20